{"tid":1356361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好市民報案] 舉報何君堯及石鏡泉涉及＜串謀及煽惑他人犯罪＞","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:39:54.000Z","uid":38842,"like":157,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5ac81f5ca92e789cc84b522bdb24f67c92dbab","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101I條「可公訴罪行（包括串謀及煽惑他人犯罪）的懲罰」的結合。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">按第101I條，煽惑他人犯罪，最高刑罰為入獄7年。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n&quot;何君堯及石鏡泉煽動白衣人攻擊市民。<br />\n證據：<br />\n石鏡泉煽惑片段　&mdash;　<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/videos/612306682630802/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchuhoidick%2Fvideos%2F612306682630802%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=aab48bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/videos/612306682630802/</a><br />\n何君堯勾結白衫黑社會資料　&mdash;　<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/354603/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%90%91%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%B1%8E%E6%8B%87%E6%8C%87-%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6%E4%BD%A0-%E4%BD%A0%E5%93%8B%E4%BF%82%E6%88%91%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F354603%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B1%258E%25E6%258B%2587%25E6%258C%2587-%25E8%25BE%259B%25E8%258B%25A6%25E4%25BD%25A0-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2593%258B%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=aba39a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/354603/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%90%91%E7%99%BD%E8%A1%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%B1%8E%E6%8B%87%E6%8C%87-%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6%E4%BD%A0-%E4%BD%A0%E5%93%8B%E4%BF%82%E6%88%91%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84</a><br />\n<br />\n證據確鑿，為表警察公正中立，請立即立案調查。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">報案網址：</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CRIME_INFMTN&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCRIME_INFMTN%26fontSize%3D100&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=69478032\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CRIME_INFMTN&amp;fontSize=100</a>"},{"pid":"5fc0f58df4f1372c32190d3d17c212b56b456f13","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"重要告示<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 您沒有義務提供您的個人資料。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2504788f1649da41e7c54eb656d8e4fcadbd8eee","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"日期: 7月21日<br />\n時間: 22:45<br />\n地點: 元朗站<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌人資料: 何君堯及石鏡泉"},{"pid":"755c317542b3d25906d89fddce2f7faa2ff1ee22","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"就係咁簡單, 我地盡咗好市民嘅責任舉報罪案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWbA1O4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWbA1O4.png&h=874ad885&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af706c18961031de4db22c627eeac8e9b19c85ec","tid":1356361,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fc0f58df4f1372c32190d3d17c212b56b456f13","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"重要告示<