84","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"起碼推到上報，等警察回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58908606c4b3cd78240bc2f48b1eaaf3a41c0dc8","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa942759a3c41ff09f2d25d282aa06494290a773","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9833184c9bb487561ebaa93be74acd757e22eeb5","tid":1356361,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2ea8ee7f7adbe40844dc84290925a4b7c22060","tid":1356361,"uid":62935,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際關係專家沈旭輝博士話<br />\n以國際定義，元朗事件係屬於 恐怖襲擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果煽動、甚至策劃 恐怖襲擊...<br />\n係國際層面，會係幾大罪？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以問一下各國際傳媒機構、及各國政府、非官方組織 等等？"},{"pid":"bee09c9cea1893fd341ea17d0c86bf546ace56af","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14cbc2653db54a17d73c7ac5cd6394e7111ac5b","tid":1356361,"uid":13125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求必須從煽惑暴動方向跟進！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"323d78d3c285d0a1474b3091997997ab99657400","tid":1356361,"uid":269452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"我想舉報樓下條燈柱畀人刑毀（寫咗警黑勾結）都未搵到警察。"},{"pid":"c0728bb39bf720b1e2175b608fb1ee13d0a3a235","tid":1356361,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94a7ec3d26e84ec079bcdd213259b7e5aa59e7f","tid":1356361,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c2066e2ebbe9683c4192f87c86709e55e7e4e2cd","tid":1356361,"uid":250804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed99876991d296dd428226a0ba989fa4e34148d","tid":1356361,"uid":13125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fmainland%2Ftext%2F2018%2F0519%2F167265.html&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=229570f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html</a><br />\n之前魚蛋都無人講話唔敢出街<br />\n今次搞到第二日幾區變死城<br />\n無得唔入暴動掛！！！<br />\n唔從暴動 同 煽惑暴動方向跟進就一定唔忿氣！"},{"pid":"99ae683bfba9c5a8c6c236adc4683282f7eb7ebe","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d2ea8ee7f7adbe40844dc84290925a4b7c22060","tid":1356361,"uid":62935,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際關係專家沈旭輝博士話<br />\n以國際定義，元朗事件係屬於 恐怖襲擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果煽動、甚至策劃 恐怖襲擊...<br />\n係國際層面，會係幾大罪？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以問一下各國際傳媒機構、及各國政府、非官方組織 等等？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap575!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap575%21zh-Hant-HK&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4a3e986c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap575!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>第575章 《聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)條例》</strong></span></span><br />\n恐怖分子財產 (terrorist property)指 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)恐怖分子或與恐怖分子有聯繫者的財產；或<br />\n(b)符合下述說明的任何其他財產 &mdash;&mdash;  (由2012年第20號第3條修訂)<br />\n(i)擬用於資助或以其他方式協助作出恐怖主義行為的；或<br />\n(ii)曾用於資助或以其他方式協助作出恐怖主義行為的；  (由2012年第20號第3條修訂)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖主義行為 (terrorist act) </span>&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)除(b)段另有規定外，指作出或恐嚇作出行動，而 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)該行動是懷有達致以下結果的意圖而進行的，或該恐嚇是懷有作出會具有達致以下結果的效果的行動的意圖而進行的 &mdash;&mdash;  (由2004年第21號第3條修訂)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(A)導致針對人的嚴重暴力；</span><br />\n(B)導致對財產的嚴重損害；<br />\n(C)危害作出該行動的人以外的人的生命；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(D)對公眾人士或部分公眾人士的健康或安全造成嚴重危險；</span><br />\n(E)嚴重干擾或嚴重擾亂電子系統的；或  (由2004年第21號第3條修訂)<br />\n(F)嚴重干擾或嚴重擾亂基要服務、設施或系統(不論是公共或私人的)的；及  (由2004年第21號第3條修訂)<br />\n(ii)該行動的作出或該恐嚇 &mdash;&mdash;  (由2004年第21號第3條修訂)<br />\n(A)的意圖是強迫特區政府或國際組織的，或是<span style=\"color: red;\">威嚇公眾人士或部分公眾人士的</span>；及  (由2012年第20號第3條修訂)<br />\n(B)是為推展政治、宗教或思想上的主張而進行的；  (由2004年第21號第3條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n**************************************************************<br />\n換言之，7月21日元朗站發生嘅事已經係恐怖襲擊。"},{"pid":"07eca2e1b88d8b6e24092efe2355163d35b041c0","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"連６１２都話係暴動<br />\n７２１點會唔係恐襲呀？"},{"pid":"ff2d8dcc1757f3896b21968acadb5dad1bfa5d26","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f96ad66de9173895a52b228903db105e40dc7d","tid":1356361,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i