"2019-07-24T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔係起唔起訴<br />\n係起訴佢乜野！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fmainland%2Ftext%2F2018%2F0519%2F167265.html&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=229570f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom大公報<br />\n  「暴動罪」在1970年訂立，屬《公安條例》第19條，指凡多於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三人使用暴力，令公眾感到恐懼或令公眾認為暴力會破壞社會安寧</span></strong></span>，即構成「參與暴動罪」，最高刑罰可判監10年。<br />\n<br />\n  「煽惑暴動罪」屬混合式檢控，是「暴動罪」與《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101I條「可公訴罪行（包括串謀及煽惑他人犯罪）的懲罰」的結合。按第101I條，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪</span></strong></span>，最高刑罰為入獄7年。"},{"pid":"9e9bc1b02af44e116287a8b7a3e45f312dc90d9d","tid":1356361,"uid":13125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"170329e43d4c3c75a90da42397b1650788e30fb7","tid":1356361,"uid":13125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c28d06ab8040e5c6fd906f0246ff38151000858","tid":1356361,"uid":158138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:19:07.000Z","msg":"David Webb以經濟日報股東身分，話應該要起訴佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔係起唔起訴<br />\n係起訴佢乜野！<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fmainland%2Ftext%2F2018%2F0519%2F167265.html&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=229570f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom大公報<br />\n  「暴動罪」在1970年訂立，屬《公安條例》第19條，指凡多於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三人使用暴力，令公眾感到恐懼或令公眾認為暴力會破壞社會安寧</span></strong></span>，即構成「參與暴動罪」，最高刑罰可判監10年。<br />\n<br />\n  「煽惑暴動罪」屬混合式檢控，是「暴動罪」與《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101I條「可公訴罪行（包括串謀及煽惑他人犯罪）的懲罰」的結合。按第101I條，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪</span></strong></span>，最高刑罰為入獄7年。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:35:26.000Z","msg":"有無議員可以跟下<br />\n毛姨姨係唔係度，我想睇到壞人受懲罰！！"},{"pid":"54025b672ac60311107c3478d130e8f0e56148f3","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a619b8b33bb5c2dd06b3b459aa7fed8054d57bc","tid":1356361,"uid":53465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"告到佢地仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4615528e2d3a79ef8b7991bc304f3c49de69d692","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a619b8b33bb5c2dd06b3b459aa7fed8054d57bc","tid":1356361,"uid":53465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"告到佢地仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5648ade84193e7d35e1c9e804b83c30dc244d13f","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dabe38be2bd8efaba40096c9b3b94bd3ba0803","tid":1356361,"uid":13125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4615528e2d3a79ef8b7991bc304f3c49de69d692","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a619b8b33bb5c2dd06b3b459aa7fed8054d57bc","tid":1356361,"uid":53465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:59:58.000Z","msg":"告到佢地仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T