9/167265.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fmainland%2Ftext%2F2018%2F0519%2F167265.html&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4fSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=229570f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/mainland/text/2018/0519/167265.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom大公報<br />\n  「暴動罪」在1970年訂立，屬《公安條例》第19條，指凡多於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三人使用暴力，令公眾感到恐懼或令公眾認為暴力會破壞社會安寧</span></strong></span>，即構成「參與暴動罪」，最高刑罰可判監10年。<br />\n<br />\n  「煽惑暴動罪」屬混合式檢控，是「暴動罪」與《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101I條「可公訴罪行（包括串謀及煽惑他人犯罪）的懲罰」的結合。按第101I條，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">煽惑他人犯罪</span></strong></span>，最高刑罰為入獄7年。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"有冇「策劃恐怖襲擊」呢條罪？<br />\n如果有的話<br />\n元朗事件應該用呢條"},{"pid":"af2ee1e027e013e94600d03968df6b6ca9c165e8","tid":1356361,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3a22fbb2951cc1181fda37c3831ff9d051b2456","tid":1356361,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae75fadb5c2cc9d92c34fe87375a198ff8c976f","tid":1356361,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"連登比人洗緊板"}]}